.TH GUIX "1" "January 2026" "GNU" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
guix \- manual page for guix lint (GNU Guix) 1.5.0rc1.47-fc2f5a
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B guix
\fI\,lint \/\fR[\fI\,OPTION\/\fR]... [\fI\,PACKAGE\/\fR]...
.SH DESCRIPTION
Run a set of checkers on the specified package; if none is specified,
run the checkers on all packages.
.TP
\fB\-c\fR, \fB\-\-checkers\fR=\fI\,CHECKER1\/\fR,CHECKER2...
only run the specified checkers
.TP
\fB\-x\fR, \fB\-\-exclude\fR=\fI\,CHECKER1\/\fR,CHECKER2...
exclude the specified checkers
.TP
\fB\-n\fR, \fB\-\-no\-network\fR
only run checkers that do not access the network
.TP
\fB\-e\fR, \fB\-\-expression\fR=\fI\,EXPR\/\fR
consider the package EXPR evaluates to
.TP
\fB\-L\fR, \fB\-\-load\-path\fR=\fI\,DIR\/\fR
prepend DIR to the package module search path
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
display this help and exit
.TP
\fB\-l\fR, \fB\-\-list\-checkers\fR
display the list of available lint checkers
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
display version information and exit
